{"title":"The Nicholas Fox Weber biography of Mondrian","link":"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/908777630/0/marginalrevolution~The-Nicholas-Fox-Weber-biography-of-Mondrian.html","date":1733214249000,"content":"<p>Definitive, this is by far the best biography of Mondrian we have or are likely to get.  I am a longstanding Mondrian fan, and have read much about him, but learned new things on virtually every page.  The book is also fun, here is one excerpt:</p>\r\n<blockquote><p>Initially Mondrian did not respond at all [to a question about surrealism].  There was prolonged silence following Breton’s inquiry.  Then, in the void, Duchamp added: “What, for example, do you think of the work of our friend Yves Tanguy here?”  Mondrian’s reply, after more thoughtful chin stroking, came firmly, but calmly: “I enjoy conversational games as much as you do, but I shall not indulge in them.  I have seen Tanguy’s exhibition at Pierre Matisse several times and found it very beautiful but very puzzling.  Yves’ work is much too Abstract for me.”</p></blockquote>\r\n<p>You can order the book <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.amazon.com/Mondrian-His-Life-Quest-Absolute/dp/0307961591/ref=sr_1_1?crid=1X3PG9S1MHJFW&amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.qUDZfosLWo-aBacB6wFFrICUVx3_ZfTWy9vb7JY628XAxFfuuWbyHd3MF5cuZnSraBzvZg4rRP0C4bpc9JGWoRXPX9LVB67UC9WllphT87OkJJBUpXXJAgcujuYI9I2yzUdc6uemZxrTLnM270k962uF_ZFKsIowhsKthp1c0_32gE9MIl7lhkixF3zaXKMqSjdXWxYBrUT9BusG9Nbha2iwqEwrwseWZ_vRUb2rBbg.ILrngFMQUrJ34HuE52iKFqaEAo1fkZlAv8FLNx4FdKI&amp;dib_tag=se&amp;keywords=nicholas+fox+weber&amp;qid=1732849048&amp;sprefix=nicholas+fox+weber%2Caps%2C118&amp;sr=8-1\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.  How is it that Weber — the author of numerous fine books on modernist art — does not have a Wikipedia page of his own?</p>\r\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/12/the-nicholas-fox-weber-biography-of-mondrian.html\">The Nicholas Fox Weber biography of Mondrian</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com\">Marginal REVOLUTION</a>.</p>\r\n<img height=\"1\" width=\"1\" src=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/i/908777630/0/marginalrevolution\" />\r\n<div><a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/28/908777630/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/fblike20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/29/908777630/marginalrevolution,\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/pinterest20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/24/908777630/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/x.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/19/908777630/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/email20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/20/908777630/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/rss20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/12/the-nicholas-fox-weber-biography-of-mondrian.html#comments\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/comments20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/12/the-nicholas-fox-weber-biography-of-mondrian.html/feed\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/commentsrss20.png\" /></a> \r\n<div><a href=\"https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/12/the-nicholas-fox-weber-biography-of-mondrian.html#comments\"><h3>Comments</h3></a><ul><li><a href=\"https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/12/the-nicholas-fox-weber-biography-of-mondrian.html#comment-160842331\">In reply to Faze.   Klint* not to be confused with Gustav Klimt ...</a> <i>by Chuck Petty</i></li><li><a href=\"https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/12/the-nicholas-fox-weber-bio